      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LOMBOK (6) is a newcomer to the Jones yard from Victoria where she showed some decent form last time in. Has not raced for four-and-a-half months but looks forward enough for the return after winning a recent trial. BET ON ACES (1) had about the mark in his first two starts off a spell before breaking the maiden at his latest appearance at Charlton, scoring by 2.5 metres from a wider draw. Kept fresh but has upside and is likely to get the favours from this nice draw. EX ELLE (2) debuted impressively last start, scoring by 5 metres at this circuit and distance. Draws lower and has plenty of scope for improvement so could take this next step. ACHY BREAKY ARK (4) didn't perform to market expectations when resuming at Canberra but strikes at 50 per cent at this circuit and distance. Fitter so worth another chance.",
